  "items": [
    {
      "id": "4e99c4e013378ec1fa8eb82daa19f4084fe307a0ae1cf2c1647d9d8bb2d25c51",
      "text": "Pixar's Core Rendering Technology"
    },
    {
      "id": "c5b28598ccb0dcc19dde7ff4f35cdf9ddda081f4e7b9634b7da20d8ce62f9517",
      "text": "For over 30 years RenderMan has been at the forefront of the visual effects revolution, and today RenderMan is a high-performance renderer built to tackle the most complicated 3D scenes imaginable."
    },
    {
      "id": "a1db7597ecb45029872f44bcbca7428c179e7acd0b968d2a34f41d329e80a383",
      "text": "With the new state-of-the-art ray tracing framework optimized for physically-based rendering, RenderMan can deliver unmatched flexibility for any production pipeline."
    },
    {
      "id": "7b08d37a195df954554715892cab0e874dc8c6781bdf1efb6826c1ea4e3f7a4d",
      "text": "About RenderMan Pro Server"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a2ae0ba2b342416f537d040e633abfa1445607629a1e4c3039b9e1aac4e638e",
      "text": "PhotoRealistic RenderMan"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe4e46e019c6c4605e24fe82a7c707336242c99ce53698a936855ae67b425d2a",
      "text": "(PRMan) is a rendering system that generates high-quality 2D images from 3D scene-description information, typically generated by a plugin to a content creation application such as Autodesk Maya. Scene descriptions are created through the RenderMan Interface and are typically comprised of:"
    },
    {
      "id": "3ca5a3bb7957053a9e1bb3c7782313023079a0528802429e53a2980ba117f762",
      "text": "a description of the geometry present in the scene like teapots, aliens, and spheres,"
    },
    {
      "id": "e9167d042c3eb65f9f2b7f015eff5a8afefeb1255f112da59cb8061d87dd79fa",
      "text": "references to functions that describe how the geometry should be shaded creating things like glass, wood, and skin,"
    },
    {
      "id": "544ec4b876726d4fbaf017b1a91381a08b962cc35bb4109280c73c9c758f02db",
      "text": "specifications of light sources (type, position, and orientation), and"
    },
    {
      "id": "7ff38f9b698dd4bd2c764e5acff7295cd5dbdf12213293a26e1fb2003fb6d8e5",
      "text": "a specification of the virtual camera through which the resultant picture is to be rendered."
    },
    {
      "id": "aa1257b62e7e704fed5a2917c1e7996519fee3443a90d3065f85588550f3bda2",
      "text": "The scene description may also specify the destination for the output image (e.g., a file or a frame buffer), as well as miscellaneous parameters that control the operation of the rendering system: how much effort to devote to avoiding"
    },
    {
      "id": "d64ff47e4273aa9c42305a40ec88314ca155e6e7e138dcc340abbfd389d1fed5",
      "text": "aliasing"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff1bfa7bc42ddea1062541520d0d016e2d216001f56564a4b3ba3d6cade9352d",
      "text": ", for instance."
    },
    {
      "id": "c63b67e93334bf73c8d6d0f286ed8bc8f6d7d5d008ce2b1f801cf6a6f30d7000",
      "text": "Scenes need not be created by hand using an editor although they can be readable by humans. Plugins are provided for popular content creation applications for an artist-friendly and efficient workflow. RenderMan's suite of plugins allows an artist to focus on creation rather than technical details."
    },
    {
      "id": "396cb4d3e641f4dbbe9aa3096072285e9d3d8116efbe221022bfc81ecf018558",
      "text": "The documentation for RenderMan covers many of these features and workflows in the form of tutorials and explanations and is ever-expanding."
    },
    {
      "id": "159ab29d78144e55b89a8a400d28de450b72c97f4a9f9e238c278b27b83b0ae1",
      "text": "Please see the below sections for plugin descriptions and tutorials:"
    },
    {
      "id": "795f02a69f755194cf3f7e203a288ed6738e53b0fe3e01ac7c41aa0b3110eba2",
      "text": "RenderMan for Maya"
    },
    {
      "id": "f433f4de7e4c7787e6c772176a0839291fd8dc33bbaa4811801c7cb94ac16d9e",
      "text": "RenderMan for Katana"
    },
    {
      "id": "44ed8e1c0f91de18ea7947df70f383124ee64b5577384abedeaf6dfbad4fca20",
      "text": "RenderMan for Houdini"
    },
    {
      "id": "18df5813b5d641c44395dafa3bf44b4883b9cc449f5134ea6e3a9de84e4a8cfa",
      "text": "RenderMan for Blender"
    }
  ]
}